<p class="ayah 53-52" id="52" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (the) people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُوحٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Nuh</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن قَبْلُ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَظْلَمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">more unjust</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَطْغَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and more rebellious.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>52<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 53-53" id="53" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْمُؤْتَفِكَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And the overturned cities</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْوَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He overthrew</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>53<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 53-54" id="54" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَغَشَّـٰهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So covered them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَشَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">covered.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>54<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
