<p class="ayah 53-59" id="59" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَمِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَدِيثِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">statement</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْجَبُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you wonder?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>59<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 53-60" id="60" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتَضْحَكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And you laugh</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَبْكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">weep?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>60<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 53-61" id="61" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">While you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَـٰمِدُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">amuse (yourselves)?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>61<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 53-62" id="62" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱسْجُدُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So prostrate</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱعْبُدُواْ ۩</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and worship (Him).</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>62<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
